OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FEvening rain
OL,6,Fand drizzle will clear east overnight
OL,7,Fwith mostly dry conditions and
OL,8,Foccasional clear spells following,
OL,9,Falthough a few showers are likely to
OL,10,Farrive across the Pennines.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FSunny spells and isolated
OL,13,Fshowers, these most likely across the
OL,14,FPennines, until late afternoon. Then
OL,15,Ffrequent showers will spread east,
OL,16,Flocally heavy with a small chance of
OL,17,Fhail and thunder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
