OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,6,Fsunshine and isolated showers. Rain
OL,7,Fand strong winds arrive overnight.
OL,8,FTuesday breezy with frequent heavy
OL,9,Fshowers. Wednesday breezy with showers
OL,10,For longer spells of rain. Temperatures
OL,11,Fnear average.
